{"tid":789783,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"艾爾文團長係咪漫畫史上最佳領袖","createTime":"2018-08-22T13:14:00.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-31T05:25:03.000Z","uid":40804,"like":51,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":31,"replies":[{"pid":"fc1e6a31efb00439903257e2ff1ae732d1d69c63","tid":789783,"uid":40804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-22T13:14:00.000Z","msg":"計謀一等一，捉女巨人果時第一次顯示才智，可惜島民對智巨因為記憶消除關係，了解嚴重不足，比女巨人走甩<br />\n<br />\n之後艾倫奪回痴撚左線，犧牲成個調查兵團都要搶到艾倫，冇埋手臂仲可以衝係最前<br />\n<br />\n王政篇比人拉鳩左，用把口嚟到爭取時間，公子獻頭<br />\n<br />\n去到瑪莉亞牆一役，中吉克計，冇哂退路絕望之際，決定放棄自己了解巨人真相既畢生夢想，慷慨就義，帶住新兵衝向吉克，幫利維聲東擊西，成功打敗猿生<br />\n<br />\n呢排睇到帕島左膠泛濫，不禁懷念艾爾文呢個聰明果斷又唔怕死既真正領袖<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d747cf23f881f6e2ab3f4bf8ea506fd1db9554a9","tid":789783,"uid":49275,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-22T13:31:23.000Z","msg":"on9"},{"pid":"2a2e4c739d0f869f406c6b9329979fad04df8cd0","tid":789783,"uid":106623,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-22T13:36:43.000Z","msg":"漫畫史上....."},{"pid":"42c9b295e5537bfc94456067573eda7433a7d289","tid":789783,"uid":85084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2a2e4c739d0f869f406c6b9329979fad04df8cd0","tid":789783,"uid":106623,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-22T13:36:43.000Z","msg":"漫畫史上....."},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-22T13:39:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"654b4929e707ae133dc54546e4b55c3ec67d1f3b","tid":789783,"uid":200521,"like":9,"dislike":39,"score":-30,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-22T13:44:25.000Z","msg":"戇鳩仔有樣睇，刀劍同巨人廚全部都係弱智<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"319d63ac3dff09c806867821f47d8c206a4f3c2f","tid":789783,"uid":1751,"like":24,"dislike":2,"score":22,"quote":{"pid":"2a2e4c739d0f869f406c6b9329979fad04df8cd0","tid":789783,"uid":106623,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-22T13:36:43.000Z","msg":